### 🐛 TROUBLESHOOTING RÁPIDO

#### Health Check 500
```bash
# 1. Ver logs
pm2 logs inmova-app --lines 50 | grep -i error

# 2. Verificar runtime
grep "export const runtime" app/api/health/route.ts

# 3. Test Prisma
cd /opt/inmova-app && node -e "const {prisma} = require('./lib/db'); prisma.\$queryRaw\`SELECT 1\`.then(console.log)"
```

#### PM2 No Carga Variables
```bash
# 1. Verificar ecosystem.config.js existe
cat /opt/inmova-app/ecosystem.config.js

# 2. Restart completo
pm2 delete inmova-app
pm2 kill
pm2 start ecosystem.config.js --env production
pm2 save

# 3. Verificar vars cargadas
pm2 env inmova-app
```

#### Build Falla en Producción
```bash
# 1. Limpiar cache
rm -rf .next
rm -rf node_modules/.cache

# 2. Regenerar Prisma
npx prisma generate

# 3. Build con logs
npm run build 2>&1 | tee build.log

# 4. Si falla por secrets, usar placeholder
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://placeholder@localhost:5432/placeholder" npm run build
```

