## 🆕 CI/CD PIPELINE (Mar 2026)

### GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/ci.yml`)
```
Push/PR to main →
  1. 🔍 Lint (ESLint)
  2. 🧪 Test (Vitest, ~1050 tests)
  3. 🏗️ Build (Next.js)
  4. 🔒 Security Audit (npm audit)
```

### Vitest Config
- **Thresholds**: 80% (lines, functions, statements), 75% (branches)
- **Pool**: forks (maxForks: 2)
- **Timeout**: 10s per test
- **Exclusiones**: e2e/, playwright specs, node_modules

### Tests Clave
```
__tests__/lib/market-opportunities.test.ts  → 10 tests (fuentes mercado)
__tests__/lib/investment-calculators.test.ts → 11 tests (hipoteca/fiscal/sensibilidad)
__tests__/lib/account-lockout.test.ts       → 6 tests (lockout behavior)
__tests__/lib/file-validation.test.ts       → 8 tests (magic bytes)
```

